item.title: Will ASML create 100+ jobs in Hutto, Texas by Q4 2026?
item.description: ASML's 35,000 sq ft Hutto lease with plans for 100+ jobs at $85K average salary. With â‚¬30-35B 2025 revenue and 100% EUV monopoly, the Dutch semiconductor giant is expanding in Texas. Market resolves YES if job target met.

resolution.rules: Market resolves YES if ASML's Hutto, Texas facility has 100 or more active employees by December 31, 2026. Resolution requires official ASML press releases, Texas Workforce Commission data, or verified employment records showing the facility has reached the 100-employee threshold.
